      <acqinfo id="aspace_be52928baf4bcaf55aaf069655c3cf74">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>The collection was a gift from the estate of Frederick J. Mahaffey, 2012-2013.</p>
      </acqinfo>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_e09be3ff8860645ebf48a9fd083fbda8">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>The materials are open for research.</p>
      </accessrestrict>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_a3f62c17836c6218a325fc7ecc96e7ac">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The collection consists of correspondence, photographs, and memorabilia relating to Frederick J. Mahaffey, BArch, 1953.  Included are letters written to a friend, George Browner Cash, BArch 1956; photographs of a student architecture project to build a geodesic dome; eulogy by Mahaffey for Nelson J. Palmer, BArch 1953; and related academic materials.</p>
      </scopecontent>
      <odd id="aspace_061692d287c278abc58ef1f72dd65929">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>The collection forms part of Yale Record Group 45 (YRG 45), Yale objects and memorabilia.</p>
      </odd>
      <arrangement id="aspace_4869905521fb207f8a4a49f3393e811a">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The collection is arranged by accession.</p>
      </arrangement>
